      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented unit tests and regression suite; formal release qualification for hemolysis-relevant turbulence models.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled and unit-tested; however, the regression suite does not cover the power-law hemolysis model sub-component. Achieved Gradation 3 against a required Gradation 4 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
