      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Manufactured-solution or benchmark verification of all governing equations including hemolysis transport; formal order-of-accuracy confirmation.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to Navier-Stokes; hemolysis scalar transport verified only against a simplified pipe-flow benchmark. Order of accuracy confirmed for momentum but not for the hemolysis source term. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
