      "rationale": "Two replicates available for three of five operating points; one replicate only for the two highest-flow points. Inter-sample CV reported as 12–18%. Sample provenance (blood analogue batch records) partially documented. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
